snippet.title: Childe/Tartaglia - Snezhnaya's Greatest Love Machine
snippet.description:
Heeeyoo!

Only another small edit I suddenly got motivation for :D This song was done by the voice actor Griffin Burns of Childe in Genshin, he recently released this on Tiktok, which is quite catchy to listen to (I wish for a full version haha) Hell yeah, I wanna bath in his voice! *totally not simping*

Here you can find Griffin Burns: https://vm.tiktok.com/ZMe19fGLq/
Game: Genshin Impact / Mihoyo
https://genshin.mihoyo.com/en/home
Original Song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YgGzAKP_HuM
(Edit: Surpisingly, the original was taken down, however you probably can still find reuploads of the song as like a 1 hour version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vGqb4oHeMAc)

- Kuri
